WEBVTT

01:40.670 --> 01:45.920
[Speed and Love]

01:46.330 --> 01:48.770
[Episode 4]

01:49.300 --> 01:50.990
[Speeding Auto House]

01:53.550 --> 01:55.680
[Episode 4]

02:48.410 --> 02:49.340
It's about time.

02:49.350 --> 02:50.750
We can't wait any longer.

03:17.140 --> 03:18.050
Sister.

03:19.430 --> 03:20.430
What's wrong?

03:23.340 --> 03:24.990
Why are you crying?

03:26.220 --> 03:27.990
Do you know where Jin Zhao is?

03:57.870 --> 03:58.660
Thank you.

05:44.909 --> 05:46.110
Why didn't you leave?

05:47.390 --> 05:49.590
Because I forgot to tell you something.

06:02.910 --> 06:04.030
Happy birthday,

06:04.740 --> 06:05.660
Zhao.

06:24.340 --> 06:30.780
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

06:30.950 --> 06:34.100
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

06:34.750 --> 06:37.280
Come on,
let's blow out the candles together.

06:41.659 --> 06:43.860
Zhao, when is your birthday?

06:51.909 --> 06:53.150
Then just let Jin Zhao and Jin Mu

06:53.150 --> 06:55.150
share the same birthday from now on.

06:55.409 --> 06:57.610
Mu's birthday will be Zhao's birthday.

06:57.740 --> 07:00.200
Together from dawn till dusk,
never to part.

07:32.540 --> 07:34.000
Happy birthday to you too.

07:37.060 --> 07:37.820
Mu.

07:53.930 --> 07:55.930
You haven't eaten all day, have you?

08:02.170 --> 08:03.050
Wait for me.

08:04.340 --> 08:05.710
I'll take you out to eat.

08:27.950 --> 08:28.880
You cried again?

08:30.780 --> 08:31.860
How did you know?

08:33.940 --> 08:35.940
Your eyes are swollen like walnuts.

08:38.230 --> 08:40.690
The more you rub them,
the worse they'll get.

08:41.539 --> 08:42.940
It's all your fault.

08:45.030 --> 08:45.940
Why blame me?

08:47.300 --> 08:48.430
I'm not telling you.

08:50.630 --> 08:51.150
If you don't tell me,

08:51.150 --> 08:53.210
how can I know if it's really my fault?

08:55.150 --> 08:56.480
Who told you I was there?

08:58.780 --> 08:59.700
Jin Xin.

09:00.700 --> 09:02.560
That kid is better than Jin Qiang.

09:09.540 --> 09:10.660
Are you doing well

09:12.310 --> 09:13.310
here?

09:15.150 --> 09:16.110
What do you mean

09:17.150 --> 09:18.110
by "well"?

09:18.990 --> 09:19.870
I mean,

09:20.910 --> 09:21.990
are you adjusting?

09:23.270 --> 09:24.630
After Jin Xin was born,

09:25.630 --> 09:27.540
do you feel like you don't belong?

09:30.660 --> 09:31.350
It's fine.

09:33.410 --> 09:34.870
What do you mean by "fine"?

09:38.060 --> 09:38.870
I'm used to it.

09:49.030 --> 09:49.700
Let's go.

09:50.760 --> 09:52.160
I'll take you somewhere.

10:03.910 --> 10:05.030
Do you have any cake left?

10:05.030 --> 10:05.660
Yes, we do.

10:06.150 --> 10:07.110
Please come in.

10:15.390 --> 10:16.060
At this hour,

10:16.060 --> 10:17.660
all the pastry chefs have gone home.

10:17.660 --> 10:18.750
See if there's anything you like.

10:18.750 --> 10:20.580
If not, we can try somewhere else.

10:20.580 --> 10:22.780
I'll take this strawberry cake then.

10:26.390 --> 10:28.580
Could you please box up
this strawberry cake for me?

10:28.580 --> 10:29.420
Just a moment.

10:32.420 --> 10:34.220
Is there anything else you want?

10:35.230 --> 10:36.510
Can I have a drink?

10:38.540 --> 10:39.180
Sure.

10:39.750 --> 10:41.680
Birthday girl gets what she wants.

11:15.780 --> 11:16.780
Make a wish now.

11:23.940 --> 11:24.870
You make one too.

11:29.920 --> 11:31.870
When is your actual birthday?

11:35.460 --> 11:36.520
It doesn't matter.

11:37.990 --> 11:39.350
How can it not matter?

11:40.000 --> 11:40.820
That was the first day

11:40.820 --> 11:42.990
you truly came into this world.

11:44.980 --> 11:47.640
I've gone over 20 years
without caring about it.

11:48.110 --> 11:49.110
I only know

11:49.850 --> 11:51.650
the day you came into this world.

11:59.850 --> 12:00.650
What's wrong?

12:02.460 --> 12:04.050
You're not going to cry, are you?

12:04.050 --> 12:04.930
No.

12:07.060 --> 12:08.540
I just suddenly feel

12:08.820 --> 12:10.110
so sorry for you.

12:10.250 --> 12:16.650
♪ Perhaps the weather's damp and mild ♪

12:15.350 --> 12:16.300
It's okay.

12:16.670 --> 12:20.500
♪ Perhaps it's about the habit
of bearing ♪

12:20.700 --> 12:21.780
The candle is about to go out.

12:21.220 --> 12:24.500
♪ A certain bitter emotion ♪

12:23.630 --> 12:24.490
Make a wish now.

12:24.520 --> 12:30.590
♪ For you, it's all too easy ♪

12:31.540 --> 12:37.250
♪ To be happy or heartbroken,
as transparent as I can be ♪

12:31.630 --> 12:32.580
The first wish

12:32.750 --> 12:34.580
needs to be said aloud to come true.

12:34.580 --> 12:35.870
I wish we

12:36.150 --> 12:37.210
could soon find out

12:37.270 --> 12:38.940
when your actual birthday is.

12:38.250 --> 12:44.150
♪ Crossing the line for love,
I've walked 1,000 km ♪

12:45.490 --> 12:51.650
♪ Brave enough to be sure is my instinct ♪

12:51.810 --> 12:52.960
♪ I believe ♪

12:52.980 --> 12:57.150
♪ Maybe it just takes a little resolve ♪

12:56.580 --> 12:57.750
As for the second wish,

12:57.410 --> 13:00.640
♪ To turn wishes into shooting stars ♪

12:58.060 --> 12:59.420
I won't say it out loud,

12:59.700 --> 13:01.660
or it won't come true.

13:01.220 --> 13:06.250
♪ Mirroring the eyes that gaze at me ♪

13:03.580 --> 13:04.700
For my second wish,

13:05.230 --> 13:08.020
may every year bring us such joy,

13:08.270 --> 13:09.870
and every moment such bliss,

13:09.990 --> 13:12.460
together from dawn till dusk,
never to part.

13:20.030 --> 13:25.850
♪ The crash of waves comes and goes ♪

13:22.930 --> 13:23.760
Eat the cake.

13:26.870 --> 13:30.350
♪ After leaning on you and hesitation ♪

13:30.460 --> 13:31.300
Thank you.

13:30.570 --> 13:33.850
♪ I've never been so steadfast and true ♪

13:33.230 --> 13:34.060
You eat too.

13:34.010 --> 13:39.850
♪ My love needs to stay clear-eyed ♪

13:35.180 --> 13:36.180
I'm not used to it.

13:36.870 --> 13:37.730
It's too sweet.

13:40.900 --> 13:46.850
♪ After the scorching ache,
I still reach for a sincere heart ♪

13:44.390 --> 13:45.540
Just to let you know in advance,

13:45.540 --> 13:47.140
I don't handle alcohol well.

13:47.510 --> 13:49.150
I might act crazy if I drink too much.

13:48.200 --> 13:54.100
♪ Crossing the line for love,
I've walked 1,000 km ♪

13:53.060 --> 13:54.110
Then should I

13:55.460 --> 14:01.600
♪ Brave enough to be sure is my instinct ♪

13:56.230 --> 13:57.560
open this bottle or not?

14:01.620 --> 14:06.740
♪ I believe
maybe it just takes a little resolve ♪

14:02.460 --> 14:04.260
Maybe we shouldn't open it then.

14:07.010 --> 14:10.350
♪ To turn wishes into shooting stars ♪

14:09.230 --> 14:10.490
Drink it if you want to.

14:10.960 --> 14:15.350
♪ Mirroring the eyes that gaze at me ♪

14:11.630 --> 14:12.830
I'll be there for you.

14:15.370 --> 14:20.460
♪ Fearless as a moth
darting into the fire ♪

14:16.870 --> 14:17.580
Come on.

14:18.420 --> 14:19.350
Happy birthday.

14:20.490 --> 14:28.550
♪ I'd rewrite the ending
of missed chances 1,000 times ♪

14:29.640 --> 14:35.190
♪ Crossing the line for love,
I've walked 1,000 km ♪

14:35.780 --> 14:36.630
I'm so happy.

14:36.790 --> 14:42.690
♪ Brave enough to be sure is my instinct ♪

14:37.030 --> 14:38.150
After all these years,

14:38.150 --> 14:41.280
I never thought
I'd celebrate a birthday with you again.

14:42.710 --> 14:43.910
♪ I believe ♪

14:44.100 --> 14:47.950
♪ Maybe it just takes a little resolve ♪

14:46.350 --> 14:48.910
That Chris is so old.

14:47.980 --> 14:51.900
♪ To turn wishes into shooting stars ♪

14:49.300 --> 14:50.430
Besides being rich,

14:50.460 --> 14:52.870
he has absolutely no other good qualities.

14:52.090 --> 14:57.130
♪ Mirroring the eyes that gaze at me ♪

14:53.270 --> 14:55.580
Mom still wants to go back
to Canada with him.

14:55.580 --> 14:58.390
I'm really worried Mom is being deceived.

14:58.870 --> 15:01.070
Your mother isn't someone who settles.

15:01.310 --> 15:03.740
She didn't find anyone else
after splitting with Jin Qiang.

15:02.880 --> 15:09.700
♪ Crossing the orbit,
stepping into your life ♪

15:04.340 --> 15:06.200
This time, she must truly like him

15:07.300 --> 15:08.630
to agree to marry again.

15:09.150 --> 15:10.880
You should trust her judgment.

15:16.390 --> 15:18.870
You call Dad "Jin Qiang"

15:18.990 --> 15:20.230
instead of "Dad."

15:20.820 --> 15:24.870
You refer to Jiang Yinghan
as "your mother" rather than "Mom."

15:26.540 --> 15:28.600
You've known all along, haven't you?

15:31.050 --> 15:32.850
When I went to Jin Qiang's house,

15:35.870 --> 15:37.330
you weren't even born yet.

15:50.180 --> 15:52.240
What about you? When did you find out?

15:53.060 --> 15:54.520
I've known for a long time.

16:03.920 --> 16:05.980
What did you think after finding out?

16:28.770 --> 16:31.220
Mom sold the old house in Nanjing.

16:31.460 --> 16:32.540
I might really

16:32.540 --> 16:34.750
have nowhere to go anymore.

16:36.750 --> 16:40.040
I won't really become homeless, will I?

16:43.750 --> 16:45.150
What are you laughing at?

16:58.180 --> 17:00.780
I suddenly feel so pitiful.

17:01.580 --> 17:04.109
Dad doesn't care about me,
Mom doesn't want me,

17:04.109 --> 17:05.710
and Brother doesn't love me.

17:10.849 --> 17:12.250
Brother doesn't love me.

17:20.180 --> 17:21.510
What do you want me to do?

17:41.400 --> 17:42.050
Let's go.

17:43.110 --> 17:43.970
Time to go home.

17:44.480 --> 17:46.320
No, I don't want to go back yet.

17:48.680 --> 17:51.280
That habit of staying out all night
isn't good.

17:53.630 --> 17:55.700
I am not with a bad person.

17:58.160 --> 18:00.090
How do you know I'm not a bad person?

18:00.700 --> 18:03.390
Well, you haven't done anything bad to me.

18:09.390 --> 18:10.990
Did you bring your house key?

18:12.220 --> 18:13.350
What a coincidence.

18:13.600 --> 18:15.080
I didn't bring it.

18:19.390 --> 18:20.520
What a coincidence.

18:22.220 --> 18:23.330
I have a spare one.

18:30.360 --> 18:32.090
It's raining heavily outside.

18:32.980 --> 18:35.710
It would be troublesome
to go out in this weather.

18:35.940 --> 18:36.910
I have a car.

18:39.830 --> 18:42.070
Can't we wait until the rain stops?

18:42.260 --> 18:43.220
Bargaining?

18:44.740 --> 18:46.200
I've had too much to drink.

18:47.390 --> 18:48.990
Let's go. It's getting late.

18:51.850 --> 18:54.490
Does your offer still stand?

18:55.110 --> 18:55.910
What offer?

18:56.400 --> 18:57.640
Letting me stay here.

19:14.890 --> 19:16.130
I'm not your brother.

19:17.980 --> 19:19.840
Do you think this is appropriate?

19:20.870 --> 19:21.940
Yes, it's fine.

19:22.470 --> 19:24.260
The water heater at Dad's place is broken.

19:24.260 --> 19:25.920
I can't even take a hot shower.

19:26.150 --> 19:28.700
You know how hot it is here.

19:28.790 --> 19:30.390
If I can't shower before bed,

19:30.390 --> 19:31.980
it'll be very uncomfortable.

19:31.980 --> 19:33.180
I'm new here.

19:33.180 --> 19:35.870
I can't handle cold water showers.

19:45.290 --> 19:46.150
Just one night.

20:12.310 --> 20:12.940
Oh no.

20:13.100 --> 20:14.370
Why am I so unlucky?

20:14.640 --> 20:16.640
Having my period at a time like this.

20:26.260 --> 20:28.260
I've left some clothes here for you.

20:34.880 --> 20:35.680
What's wrong?

20:39.370 --> 20:40.700
Does your stomach hurt?

20:45.070 --> 20:47.070
Is your stomach upset from the beer?

21:00.350 --> 21:01.310
Are you...

21:01.330 --> 21:02.290
Yes.

21:03.500 --> 21:04.420
That's right.

21:04.720 --> 21:05.520
That's right.

21:06.010 --> 21:08.320
But it seems we can't order takeout here.

21:10.660 --> 21:11.590
You take a shower first.

21:11.590 --> 21:12.520
I'll go buy some.

21:16.360 --> 21:18.420
What are you buying today, handsome?

21:18.630 --> 21:20.830
Please support my business more often.

21:23.550 --> 21:24.940
Do you need any help?

21:26.530 --> 21:28.730
Just let me know if you need assistance.

21:28.790 --> 21:30.190
Did you get the right one?

21:37.870 --> 21:39.980
Would you like
to join our 10-baht promotion?

21:39.980 --> 21:44.460
Just add 10 more baht.

21:45.040 --> 21:48.910
You can choose anything from this shelf.

21:49.650 --> 21:50.580
It's a good deal.

21:59.250 --> 22:00.910
I bought everything you need.

22:01.390 --> 22:02.450
I'll wait outside.

22:02.500 --> 22:04.100
Call me if you need anything.

22:23.930 --> 22:25.610
I'm done. You can shower now.

22:43.320 --> 22:46.050
I'll give you these slippers
after I get into bed.

22:59.530 --> 23:00.730
Where will you sleep?

23:00.800 --> 23:01.520
Next door.

23:08.000 --> 23:09.060
At Sanlai's place.

23:09.940 --> 23:10.800
Get some sleep.

23:42.020 --> 23:42.820
What's wrong?

23:43.940 --> 23:45.020
My stomach hurts.

23:46.700 --> 23:47.610
I'll take you to the hospital.

23:47.610 --> 23:48.450
No need.

23:50.110 --> 23:52.630
It's my period. It'll get better soon.

24:00.090 --> 24:01.090
Does it hurt a lot?

24:10.770 --> 24:11.570
Wait a moment.

24:13.420 --> 24:14.390
It says here

24:15.120 --> 24:17.050
you should warm it with your hands.

24:22.330 --> 24:23.530
Then press

24:24.020 --> 24:25.350
the Guanyuan acupoint.

24:25.550 --> 24:27.150
Where is the Guanyuan acupoint?

24:27.150 --> 24:28.010
It's about 10 cm

24:28.180 --> 24:29.830
right below your navel.

24:32.020 --> 24:33.180
It's not working.

24:33.700 --> 24:34.460
Press with your finger.

24:34.460 --> 24:35.790
I am pressing it.

24:37.750 --> 24:38.470
It's here.

24:46.980 --> 24:49.740
Your hands are so warm. Warm me up.

25:03.390 --> 25:04.500
Feeling better?

25:10.440 --> 25:11.770
Don't move.

26:01.940 --> 26:03.590
Why did you bring him back?

26:04.180 --> 26:06.070
Don't you know our situation?

26:06.500 --> 26:07.740
I'm pregnant.

26:08.350 --> 26:09.460
How can I manage?

26:09.560 --> 26:10.980
Can you afford to raise him?

26:10.980 --> 26:13.460
One more child just means
one more set of dishes.

26:13.460 --> 26:14.840
You're making a fuss over nothing.

26:14.840 --> 26:15.910
Easy for you to say.

26:15.930 --> 26:17.430
Is it just about an extra set of dishes?

26:17.430 --> 26:18.500
Can you really support him?

26:18.500 --> 26:19.830
Charles was my brother.

26:19.920 --> 26:21.110
He had an accident at the racetrack.

26:21.110 --> 26:22.570
I can't abandon his child!

26:22.630 --> 26:23.940
His father was just a daredevil!

26:23.940 --> 26:25.180
I'm a daredevil too!

26:25.590 --> 26:26.150
You...

26:28.630 --> 26:30.150
Jin Qiang, let me tell you.

26:30.660 --> 26:31.920
I don't agree with this.

26:31.920 --> 26:33.120
Do whatever you want.

26:37.430 --> 26:39.690
You just gave birth
and don't even take care of your baby.

26:39.690 --> 26:41.550
You always run off to dance class.

26:41.780 --> 26:43.020
What else can I do?

26:43.110 --> 26:44.840
We still need to live our lives.

26:44.910 --> 26:46.770
I need to earn money for my family.

26:48.430 --> 26:49.180
I'm done talking to you.

26:49.180 --> 26:50.910
The baby's awake. I need to breastfeed.

26:50.910 --> 26:51.550
That's it.

26:55.260 --> 26:56.020
Sweetheart.

27:10.020 --> 27:11.820
My daughter is almost 2 years old

27:12.240 --> 27:13.870
and still can't talk.

27:14.460 --> 27:15.870
I'm really worried.

27:16.730 --> 27:17.730
I don't know

27:17.770 --> 27:19.900
if it has something to do with Jin Zhao.

27:20.490 --> 27:21.380
I just feel like

27:21.410 --> 27:23.250
my life isn't going well.

27:23.270 --> 27:24.400
You know what I mean?

27:28.740 --> 27:29.410
Anyway...

27:31.050 --> 27:32.310
I've already decided.

27:37.530 --> 27:39.190
Thank you for your help, Miss.

27:40.310 --> 27:41.070
Jin Zhao,

27:41.590 --> 27:43.910
you must listen to your teacher there

27:44.030 --> 27:46.130
and get along with the other children.

27:46.130 --> 27:48.460
I'll come visit you when I can, okay?

27:50.860 --> 27:52.720
Miss, I'll leave him in your care.

27:53.260 --> 27:53.910
Come.

27:55.550 --> 27:56.870
Brother.

28:03.120 --> 28:04.430
Brother.

28:10.110 --> 28:12.290
[Speeding Auto House]

28:15.500 --> 28:16.070
Master,

28:16.220 --> 28:17.780
why are you starting work so early today?

28:17.780 --> 28:20.240
Want some coconut juice?
It's really fresh.

28:20.910 --> 28:21.700
Keep it down.

28:23.070 --> 28:24.000
I don't want any.

28:24.110 --> 28:25.090
Then I'll take it inside.

28:25.090 --> 28:25.750
Don't go in.

28:28.740 --> 28:29.740
Who's in there?

28:30.870 --> 28:31.910
A heavy sleeper.

28:34.220 --> 28:35.420
A heavy sleeper?

28:37.280 --> 28:38.910
Brandy, Yang.

28:39.590 --> 28:40.310
Breakfast is ready.

28:40.310 --> 28:41.520
I bought it from miles away.

28:41.520 --> 28:42.590
Be quiet.

28:42.980 --> 28:43.780
What's wrong?

28:43.870 --> 28:44.940
There's someone in Master's room.

28:44.940 --> 28:45.940
Someone's there?

28:46.780 --> 28:47.500
Who is it?

28:48.590 --> 28:49.660
I don't know.

28:50.190 --> 28:52.070
Seems someone has stayed in the lounge
since last night.

28:52.070 --> 28:53.660
Doesn't he forbid others
from staying in his room?

28:53.660 --> 28:55.310
Yes, who could it be?

28:57.620 --> 28:58.580
Snakey?

28:59.260 --> 29:00.020
No way.

29:00.220 --> 29:01.550
Last time she came to the shop,

29:01.550 --> 29:02.730
she insisted on going to the lounge

29:02.730 --> 29:04.860
and casually lay down on Brandy's bed.

29:05.040 --> 29:06.350
When he came back,

29:06.550 --> 29:07.450
upon seeing that,

29:07.450 --> 29:09.680
he grabbed her by the collar
and threw her out.

29:09.680 --> 29:10.770
Snakey was so angry

29:11.040 --> 29:13.040
she hasn't been back for a long time.

29:13.220 --> 29:14.380
It can't be Snakey.

29:14.500 --> 29:15.410
Right.

29:17.310 --> 29:18.630
Then who could it be

29:18.980 --> 29:20.380
that he's so tolerant of?

29:40.680 --> 29:41.570
Did it start?

29:42.450 --> 29:43.700
Why is there no response?

29:43.700 --> 29:44.660
No, it didn't.

29:45.610 --> 29:47.570
What's the problem then?

29:48.190 --> 29:51.590
The spark plugs have been replaced.
What about the fuel line?

29:51.890 --> 29:53.820
It's not about the fuel line at all.

29:55.100 --> 29:55.900
The throttle?

29:56.070 --> 29:57.180
The throttle is fine.

29:57.180 --> 29:58.150
I've checked it.

29:59.440 --> 30:00.770
Then why won't it start?

30:01.140 --> 30:02.800
Have you checked the battery?

30:03.560 --> 30:04.450
Look.

30:06.570 --> 30:07.970
Could it be the fuel pump?

30:22.750 --> 30:24.190
I don't think so.

30:41.830 --> 30:43.030
-Who is it?
-Who is it?

30:44.500 --> 30:45.870
W-Who are you?

30:47.330 --> 30:48.990
Hello, I'm Jiang Mu,

30:49.020 --> 30:50.480
Jin Zhao's little sister.

31:03.350 --> 31:04.180
Your car has

31:04.200 --> 31:06.010
a loose intake pressure sensor.

31:10.700 --> 31:12.030
What are you looking at?

31:12.350 --> 31:13.280
Get back to work.

31:26.040 --> 31:27.120
Why aren't you wearing pants?

31:27.120 --> 31:28.090
I am.

31:30.570 --> 31:32.300
Is your stomach still hurting?

31:37.700 --> 31:39.120
Go change into long pants.

31:39.120 --> 31:40.850
And come out for breakfast. Go.

31:51.840 --> 31:53.120
I don't eat carrots.

31:55.970 --> 31:57.300
No green onions either.

32:02.500 --> 32:03.160
Move aside.

32:10.980 --> 32:12.180
What are you laughing at?

32:12.180 --> 32:14.110
I'm not afraid of the hot oil.

32:14.220 --> 32:15.110
I just...

32:15.160 --> 32:17.440
It just happened too suddenly.

32:18.700 --> 32:19.700
Can you cook?

32:20.630 --> 32:21.550
Of course I can.

32:22.630 --> 32:24.260
Don't underestimate me.

32:24.870 --> 32:26.660
I'm a quick learner.

32:26.800 --> 32:27.700
It's just that before,

32:27.700 --> 32:29.900
I didn't have many chances to practice.

32:37.580 --> 32:40.170
You can cook and make dumplings.

32:40.960 --> 32:42.630
Looks like you're quite good
in the kitchen.

32:42.630 --> 32:44.230
Don't think too highly of me.

32:46.500 --> 32:48.900
I just had more opportunities to practice.

33:04.150 --> 33:05.240
Do you have time later?

33:05.240 --> 33:07.760
Could you help me unpack my suitcase?

33:07.980 --> 33:09.510
All my clothes are in there.

33:13.660 --> 33:14.460
Is that okay?

33:15.550 --> 33:17.280
Did I agree to let you stay here?

33:18.830 --> 33:20.630
Didn't you say so last night?

33:22.110 --> 33:23.310
I said just one night.

33:23.550 --> 33:24.860
You've already slept here for one night.

33:24.860 --> 33:26.390
I haven't had enough sleep.

33:31.590 --> 33:32.840
That's insane.

33:33.530 --> 33:35.440
I'm starting to doubt my ears.

33:36.020 --> 33:37.070
I never thought

33:37.260 --> 33:38.660
Master would finally...

33:40.350 --> 33:42.180
Find love at last.

33:45.530 --> 33:47.290
Can I stay a few more nights?

33:55.990 --> 33:56.750
No way.

34:02.450 --> 34:04.780
How about 2 nights? Not counting tonight.

34:15.540 --> 34:16.940
Finish your vegetables.

34:17.230 --> 34:18.760
Don't pick out the carrots.

34:18.940 --> 34:20.870
You're so stubborn.

34:21.020 --> 34:22.280
You're not my brother.

34:22.679 --> 34:24.080
You're too controlling.

35:16.840 --> 35:17.550
Lin Sui,

35:18.130 --> 35:18.980
we've checked all surveillance footage

35:18.980 --> 35:20.110
from that night on the mountain,

35:20.110 --> 35:22.440
but couldn't find any clear facial shots.

35:40.880 --> 35:43.140
The other cars have been left far behind.

36:04.950 --> 36:05.880
The 11th turn.

36:06.310 --> 36:07.640
Whose black car is that?

36:07.700 --> 36:08.620
I'm sorry, Lin Sui.

36:08.620 --> 36:09.620
It's not one of ours.

36:09.620 --> 36:10.890
The road probably
hasn't been properly blocked off.

36:10.890 --> 36:12.490
It's just a passing vehicle.

37:06.250 --> 37:08.480
♪ Make it fast, never slow down ♪

37:08.500 --> 37:10.980
♪ Show off my extraordinary form ♪

37:11.000 --> 37:12.120
♪ Speeding love ♪

37:12.140 --> 37:13.540
♪ Whether I succeed or fail ♪

37:13.560 --> 37:15.710
♪ I just want to be free ♪

37:15.740 --> 37:18.560
♪ Make my name be known
throughout the world ♪

37:18.580 --> 37:20.660
♪ You just wait and see ♪

37:21.060 --> 37:24.060
That car's got over 1,000 HP
and 2,000 lb-ft of torque.

37:25.140 --> 37:28.140
By the sound, it's not an ordinary rotor.

37:28.350 --> 37:30.270
A two-rotor, three-rotor,

37:30.580 --> 37:31.500
or even

37:31.910 --> 37:33.620
a four-rotor is possible.

37:33.980 --> 37:35.100
But we've checked

37:35.100 --> 37:35.910
the largest modified car gatherings

37:35.910 --> 37:37.190
in Manshi,

37:37.750 --> 37:39.610
but couldn't find that black car.

37:39.810 --> 37:41.850
Then find the person.

37:42.240 --> 37:43.670
In Southeast Asia, no more than 5 people

37:43.670 --> 37:45.190
can fabricate

37:45.210 --> 37:46.920
a two-rotor or more.

37:47.270 --> 37:48.710
Go out on the streets now.

37:48.870 --> 37:51.670
When you hear a rotor sound, open the hood

37:51.690 --> 37:52.820
and check one by one.

37:54.580 --> 37:55.780
What are you waiting for?

37:55.780 --> 37:56.540
Hurry up!

37:58.250 --> 37:59.050
Got it.

38:07.870 --> 38:10.130
Even if I have to turn Manshi upside down,

38:10.250 --> 38:12.040
I will find you.
